node.text: I wanted to let my friend @theslaygawd take over for my page to share his voice and experiences... Thank you Ryan for being so brave to speak on this and having the tough discussion that everyone needs to hear and have. We all need to be apart of the change and we need to remember that this is a movement not a moment. #BLM

node.text:
I had my friends go in public and play people my song without them knowing it was "Jake Paul" to see their true and honest reactions. People like to judge my music with bias because of the shit songs I have put out in the past, but we are taking this seriously now and I want people to enjoy my music and not just judge it because of my name... These reactions were CRAZY.
My new music video drops tomorrow at 12PM PST. PRE SAVE WITH THE LINK IN BIO.

node.text: Tyron is getting added to my sleepy meme collection Sunday August 29th be there in person Ohio or watch live on PPV @showtimeboxing

Today launching my non profit charity foundation @boxingbullies was a surreal moment and truly a dream come true.. Today we talked about our initiative to fight back against bullying, put the kids through a 50 minute tough boxing workout, sponsored 15 amateur fights, and gave away over 100 pairs of gloves.. Boxing has helped me learn so much about myself and realize what’s important in life.. I want to share this beautiful sport with as many kids as possible.. Our mission is to instill confidence, leadership, and courage in the youth through the sport of Boxing and to get Boxing gloves into to as many kids hands as possible across the world, while fighting back against the ever increasing problem of bullying and cyber bullying in our generation.. WE NEED YOU, POSITIVITY, AND ALL THE HELP WE CAN GET TO TACKLE THIS PROBLEM.. Thank you to the Puerto Rico Amateur Boxing federation, Team Problem Child, and everyone who helped and came out to this event. Follow the @boxingbullies page to help out, keep up, and because we might be coming to a city near you soon🥊

node.text: CLEVELAND. ITS SHOWTIME. TICKETS ARE OFFICIALLY NOW ON SALE (link in bio) come see me take on former UFC Champion Tyron Woodley LIVE Sunday August 29th. Tickets start at just $10 dollars as I wanted to make it easy for anyone to come to a big show Pay Per View event🤟🏼. It’s a dream come true to bring this one home and be fighting in the arena I grew up watching the Cavs….This card will be one of the most electric nights of the year and is already stacked with some of Cleveland’s best fighters @charlesconwell & @montana2prettylove and from Puerto Rico 🇵🇷 the superstar champion @serranosisters taking on Mexican champion @yamilethmercadooficial - SEE Y’ALL THERE👊🏼
